This Project is intended to run locally through XAMPP as it was a university project,I have hosted it locally in my system and presented it in the university
To run this project in your device:-
1)install XAMPP
2)Transfer the entire project to the htdocs folder of XAMPP folder
3)Start the XAMPP control panel's Apache and MySQL
4)Now open any browser and type localhost/FOLDER_NAME
REFERENCE:https://timetoprogram.com/run-php-project-xampp/
